      • processOrder

        public boolean processOrder(Order order,
                   PublicArgument[] args)
                     throws StockException,
                            WrongArgumentListException,
                            InvalidArgumentException
        Processes an order for a stock in this warehouse
        Parameters:
        order - the order to process
        args - the arguments to process this stock with
        Throws:
        StockException - the stock which processed this order was full
        WrongArgumentListException - the arguments didn't meet the requirements for the item for which this order was made
        InvalidArgumentException - thrown if the list or one of the arguments is null, or if the answer does not satisfy the constraints.
